 types of cats.\nIn this game, you can do more than just leisurely observe free-spirited cats; you can play with them using a cat teaser, stroke their bellies, and even pick them up for a cuddle.\nAt the delightful yard location, home to uniquely charming cats like \"Calico cat,\" \"Odd-eyed cat,\" and \"Big fat cat,\" you are sure to encounter your purrfect feline companion.\nEnjoy the uninterrupted \"Life with Cats\" to the fullest.", "short_description": "Get Closer to the World of Cats!\n\n\"Neko Atsume Purrfect\" is a simulation game featuring a whopping 46 different types of cats.\nIn this game, you can do more than just leisurely observe free-spirited cats; you can play with them using a cat teaser, stroke their bellies, and even pick them up for a cuddle.\nAt the delightful yard location, home to uniquely charming cats like \"Calico cat,\" \"Odd-eyed cat,\" and \"Big fat cat,\" you are sure to encounter your purrfect feline companion."}, {"images": {"nodes": [{"file_name": "PUB_NekoAtsumeJP_MobileIcon_512x512.png", "id": "6714534841974125", "image_type": "APP_IMG_ICON", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031338_6714534848640791_6683758679402030795_n.png?_nc_cat=102&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=2S3VTglbsV8Q7kNvgGZq9Et&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAbBFQf3Sx_KgpQjbcoV4_pveWqWnkuQeA_62kXDgFOvg&oe=66D58E68"}, {"file_name": "PUB_NekoAtsumeJP_Hero_3000x900.png", "id": "2523900887773480", "image_type": "APP_IMG_HERO", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/86597262_2523900891106813_6610753884716316438_n.png?_nc_cat=103&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=PdiYzmKUmtoQ7kNvgEzSnNN&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBOOnfoSX7u_-pVBQw6_9jijjyzZRiFq5Nbnt9jOmQMPQ&oe=66D58A6B"}, {"file_name": "PUB_NekoAtsumeJP_MiniLandscape_1080x360.png", "id": "1309605619921604", "image_type": "APP_IMG_SMALL_LANDSCAPE", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/86620217_1309605623254937_689255883300373322_n.png?_nc_cat=104&ccb=1-7&_nc_s